  "description": "The image depicts a nighttime scene of a circular fountain in a paved area, illuminated by warm lights. Behind the fountain, a grassy hill slopes upwards towards a large, modern building with many windows, also lit from within. The building appears to be multiple stories high and has a somewhat institutional or office-like design. Trees, both bare and with some foliage, are scattered throughout the scene, framing the fountain and the building. The sky is overcast and dark, contributing to a subdued, almost melancholic atmosphere. The foreground shows a paved area marked with white lines, likely a parking lot or plaza. The fountain\u2019s water jets are visible, adding a dynamic element to the otherwise still landscape.",
